              h3 Keynote Speakers
              p.text-muted Throughout the event, you will have the chance to experience an extended TEDx style talk, from top researchers and professionals across the field of Mathematics. A Field medalist, mathemagician and others are expected to join us!
          .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
