              h3 Panel Discussions
              p.text-muted To change the way Mathematics is perceived,  we will also be presenting topics for the audience to engage in through panel discussions. We plan to host 3 different discussions, and these will range from traditional questions that have troubled scientists for centuries, to the latest hot topics surrounding recent developments and new applications of Mathematics.
          .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
