              h3 Workshops
              p.text-muted For many, Mathematics might be hard to understand without a pen and paper approach or a specific problem to solve. That's why we are introducing workshops. Have you ever wondered what the numbers behind a Rubix cube are? Wanted to challenge a chess Grandmaster? What about the probabilities in poker? These are just a few more reasons to join us!
